Subtitles by KBS World

1015
01:03:04,670 --> 01:03:06,770
From now on, show me some respect.

1016
01:03:06,770 --> 01:03:07,740
What?

1017
01:03:07,750 --> 01:03:09,400
Don't worry.

1018
01:03:09,400 --> 01:03:11,540
She doesn't even know you're a woman.

1019
01:03:11,540 --> 01:03:13,080
But don't get caught.

1020
01:03:13,080 --> 01:03:14,350
Don't you have any pride?

1021
01:03:14,350 --> 01:03:15,540
You don't feel ashamed?

1022
01:03:15,540 --> 01:03:17,870
You don't feel upset about Sedal?

1023
01:03:17,880 --> 01:03:19,770
Why can't you be happy for him?

1024
01:03:19,780 --> 01:03:23,470
Take these out and throw away the trash.

1025
01:03:23,480 --> 01:03:26,880
My son Minjung, forgive your dad.

1026
01:03:26,880 --> 01:03:28,900
The best gift. What was it?

1027
